16
00:01:19,633 --> 00:01:24,433
These types of effects are also typically longer 
lasting that the magic bullet

17
00:01:24,433 --> 00:01:27,433
and hypodermic needle effects.

18
00:01:27,433 --> 00:01:32,333
3) Personal effects. Now it was appreciated that 
one audience member

19
00:01:32,333 --> 00:01:34,266
is not the same as the other.

20
00:01:34,266 --> 00:01:38,732
Effects therefore are pluriform and have to be 
studied in context. A violent cartoon 

21
00:01:38,733 --> 00:01:42,333
might have a completely different effect on a 
child that watches it alone

22
00:01:42,333 --> 00:01:46,833
than on a child that watches it with siblings or 
parents. 

23
00:01:46,833 --> 00:01:49,133
4) Reinforcement rather than change.

24
00:01:49,133 --> 00:01:54,733
Studies increasingly indicate that reinforcement 
effects are quite strong,

25
00:01:54,733 --> 00:01:57,266
people remember and process content 
selectively,

26
00:01:57,266 --> 00:02:00,766
based on their own knowledge and 
predispositions.

27
00:02:00,766 --> 00:02:06,966
Therefore things that connect with their preferred 
reality will sooner be processed.

28
