29
00:02:11,366 --> 00:02:14,732
Television was in many ways a new platform:

30
00:02:14,733 --> 00:02:19,733
it captivated its audience, created new worlds 
within a media reality.

31
00:02:19,733 --> 00:02:25,999
Television shows had a huge impact. Unlike the 
paper, people watched television together, 

32
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,700
so in many ways it was a social medium as 
well.

33
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:32,500
It was also topic for discussion.

34
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:37,633
