35
00:02:37,633 --> 00:02:40,699
Hypermediality, when people reference media 
content, 

36
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:46,900
became one way of opening yourself up or 
closing yourself of to a group. 

37
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,800
We can imagine the new co-worker

38
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:52,966
who is the only one who hasnât seen a new 
series on television. 

39
00:02:52,966 --> 00:02:56,266
